	<h2>Products and categories</h2>
	<h3>Manage Products and categories</h3>
	<p>As in most e-commerce stores, with LC you can manage your products by categories. Categories can also contain subcategories which, in turn, may have their own subcategories. The number of subcategories is unlimited.</p>

	<h3>TO DO list</h3>
	<ul>	
		<li><a href="#manage_tree">Manage category tree</a></li>	
	</ul>
	

	<a name="manage_tree" />
	<h3>Category Tree</h3>
	<p>Category tree represents how all of the categories are arranged. At the top of the tree is the Root category which is a parent category for all the descending categories. In the category tree you can easily manage your categories by selecting one of the options: </p>
	<ul>
		<li>Create a new sub-category</li>
		<li>Remove selected category</li>
		<li>Viewing content?</li>
	</ul>




	
